\includegraphics[scale=0.5]{DIS_SumSignalPlot_dataMC_Unfolded_x_z26.pdf}
\caption{\label{fig:xFe} Deep inelastic scattering events in iron as a function of unsmeared Bjorken-x. The total systematic uncertainty is drawn as a band around the simulation, and the error bars around the data are statistical.}
